Java team tool for semi-automatic creation of ebuilds from pom.xml.

Use example:

# Generate cache of java related packages from portage tree.
java-ebuilder --refresh-cache -t /usr/portage

# Find corresponding maven groupId, artifactId and version in the cache.
( echo 1.0; tail -n +2 $HOME/.java-ebuilder/cache | parallel -j -2 scripts/meta.sh; ) > cache
cp cache $HOME/.java-ebuilder/cache

# Create ebuild.
java-ebuilder -p pom.xml -e xxx.ebuild -g -u http://xxx.tg.gz --keywords amd64 --workdir .

